1
00:00:32,440 --> 00:00:33,640
Look, what's that over there?

2
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,400
What's inside?

3
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:53,160
Launch the explosive barrels!

4
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:30,800
Not good!

5
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,000
It's trying to climb up!

6
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,920
Explosive barrels!

7
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,600
Keep launching!

8
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,440
Throw them straight down!

9
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,240
Continue!

10
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:47,960
Darn it!

11
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:48,840
We can't hit it!

12
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,400
Don't stop!

13
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,360
Keep throwing them!

14
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:54,920
Small barrels of gunpowder...

15
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,160
...can't hurt it!

16
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:56,920
Stop talking!

17
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,640
Bring the large gunpowder barrel, quick!

18
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,240
Then...

19
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:10,800
I'll do it.

20
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,840
Don't!

21
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:14,320
Xiang Chong!

22
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,720
Xiang Chong goes ahead!

23
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:17,800
Brothers!

24
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,320
Defend Chentang Pass to the death!

25
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,080
Vow never to retreat!

26
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,400
No!

27
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,640
Brother Xiang!

28
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:36,760
Brother Xiang!

29
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:03,680
You dare kill my Sea Devourer?

30
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:06,080
You seek death!

31
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,880
Your Highness, no need to be hasty.

32
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,040
Your old servant still has a plan.

33
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,640
Watch out!

34
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,360
Get down and find cover!

35
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,200
They are entering Chentang Pass!

36
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,640
Darn it!

37
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,160
Long Spear Battalion!

38
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,400
Here!

39
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,240
Crown Prince!

40
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:50,320
Their arrows and catapult stones...

41
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,360
...have been exhausted.

42
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,520
Good!

43
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,400
Not good!

44
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,120
Heavens!

45
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,200
How can this be?

46
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,160
Darn it!

47
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:09,840
Heavens!

48
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,760
We can't hold it!

49
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:11,400
What do we do?

50
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,360
Darn it!

51
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,360
They are coming!

52
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:22,920
General!

53
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,680
Can we still hold Chentang Pass?

54
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,800
Keep holding on...

55
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,160
...and there will be hope.

56
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,760
Why can't we find a single one?

57
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:16,720
The Sewers of Chentang Pass extend in all directions.

58
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,440
Perhaps...

59
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,800
...their target is the civilians.

60
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,800
Fight to the death, never retreat!

61
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,400
Charge!

62
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,160
Charge!

63
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,600
Kill!

64
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,080
Defend Chentang Pass!

65
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,280
There are still many Octopus Monsters!

66
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,000
Do not let your guard down!

67
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,040
Thank you, big sister.

68
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,280
Thank you for saving me, big sister.

69
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,440
Let's go.

70
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,760
We are going to the Sewers.

71
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,240
To root them all out.

72
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,040
Weak Human Race.

73
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,960
You do not deserve to live.

74
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,320
There are too many enemies!

75
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,160
We can hardly resist!

76
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:13,800
Brothers!

77
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,360
We are the last line of defense!

78
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:17,000
Behind us lies Chentang Pass!

79
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,520
Charge!
